short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension that instantly generates and exports a website profile in just one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sinkedin Profilemap is a Chrome extension that generates a profile of the current page with a single click, and allows you to export the gathered links as a CSV file. This tool is designed for users who need a quick and easy way to obtain a profile on a webpage.
